{"tid":1944442,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 9恢復生產，最快會在 4 月底發表，業內人士指 Apple 與中國比亞迪集團簽約","createTime":"2020-03-26T11:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T07:33:11.000Z","uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6fdf2cce9fb3eaec36bbbc641eeda8b26e3326a6","tid":1944442,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"據外媒消息，因武漢肺炎疫情影響其生產進度的 iPhone 9（ iPhone SE 2）已恢復生產，預計最快會在 4 月底發表。<br />\n <br />\n受武漢肺炎影響，生產工作不斷延遲，一些核心零組件的供應不穩，導致原計劃在 3 月發佈的 iPhone 9 一直未能順利量產。不言，近日有業內人士指出，Apple 已經與中國比亞迪集團簽定新合約，以擴大生產規模和加快生產速度，但暫時未知比亞迪將會為蘋果代工哪些產品。<br />\n <br />\n而分析師 Jon Prosser 亦在其 Twitter 上爆料，指 iPhone 9 已經開始量產，更指信息可靠性為 100%。他在上週曾預測 Apple 快將推出新產品，而 Apple 的確在本週發布了新款 iPad Pro 和 MacBook Air。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBeB55B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBeB55B.png&h=8c862551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此次，Apple 即將發表的低價新 iPhone 包含兩款機型，分別是 iPhone 9 和 iPhone 9 Plus。iPhone 9 的售價預計在 3,000 人民幣（約港幣 HKD$3310 元）左右，而 iPhone 9 Plus 起步價約 3,300 人民幣（約港幣 HKD$3640 元）左右。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：ibtimes"},{"pid":"10039a906998291e58188af8efcf8feba078e7b1","tid":1944442,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"外媒勁d定中国既有關當局勁d?"},{"pid":"0581604fac3623be5c0980bb7b421e008dbb43b1","tid":1944442,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"又撚狗"},{"pid":"894b4930c60eb5281450c0745aa9ac4dcd25c3b7","tid":1944442,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0581604fac3623be5c0980bb7b421e008dbb43b1","tid":1944442,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"又撚狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"準備撚到下年3月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450392c385c5a27dee7f82a048157768728b3add","tid":1944442,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":